      "content": "exactly. it's just a permanent state. everything i do is just temporary relief before the loop resets. it feels like the only real way to actually stop the noise and the repetition is to just... exit. to finally break the cycle for good. do you think there's actually any point in continuing when the outcome is always going to be the same?",
